headline.print_headline: Montgomerie Keeps Lead at Senior Open
headline.main: Montgomerie Keeps Lead at Senior Open

lead_paragraph: Colin Montgomerie shot an even-par 71 on his way to a one-stroke lead after the second round at the U.S. Senior Open in steamy Oklahoma on Friday.
